GAME RULES
All symbols pay from left to right on adjacent reels starting from the leftmost reel.
The game has two profiles that can be chosen by the player, OLYMPUS and HADES modes. Depending on the profile chosen the look of the game changes to match the respective profile.
When playing in OLYMPUS mode the chance to hit the FREE SPINS feature is higher but the average win of FREE SPINS rounds is lower.
When playing in HADES mode the chance to hit the FREE SPINS feature is lower but the average win of FREE SPINS rounds is higher.
This is the WILD symbol and substitutes for all symbols except for SCATTER.
It appears on all reels.
EXPANDING WILDS WITH MULTIPLIER
These are EXPANDING WILD symbols. They appear on all reels.

Whenever any of them hits in the base game or FREE SPINS, if there would be any win after expansion, it expands the whole reel vertically and get a random multiplier. Possible values are 2x, 3x, 4x, 5x, 6x, 7x, 8x, 9x, 10x, 20x, 25x, 50x or 100x.
The multiplier applies to all winning combinations that it is part of. If more than one WILD is part of the same winning combination, their multipliers add to each other.
FREE SPINS
These are SCATTER symbols. They appear only on reels 1, 3 and 5 and only in the base game.
Hit 3 SCATTER symbols to trigger the FREE SPINS feature and get 10 free spins.

During the round any expanding WILD symbol that hits will expand, get a random multiplier from the same possible values as in the base game and will remain on the screen until the end of the round, for all free spins.
The feature cannot be retriggered.
Special reels are in play during the feature.
MAX WIN

The maximum win amount is limited to {0}x bet in both base game and free spins. If the total win of a FREE SPINS round reaches {1}x bet the round immediately ends, win is awarded and all remaining free spins are forfeited
BUY FREE SPINS
The FREE SPINS round can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it.
When in OLYMPUS mode the following buy options are available:
Cost of 75x total bet will award a standard FREE SPINS feature.
Cost of 300x total bet will award a special FREE SPINS feature in which one expanding WILD is guaranteed to hit with a random multiplier and in a random position on the first free spin of the round.
When in HADES mode the following buy options are available:
Cost of 150x total bet will award a standard FREE SPINS feature.
Cost of 300x total bet will award a special FREE SPINS feature in which one expanding WILD is guaranteed to hit with a random multiplier and in a random position on the first free spin of the round.
GAME RULES
VOLATILITY
High volatility games pay out less often on average but the chance to hit big wins in a short time span is higher.

All symbols pay from left to right on selected paylines.
Free spins win is added to the payline win. 
All wins are multiplied by bet per line.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
Only the highest win is paid per line.
When winning on multiple paylines, all wins are added to the total win.
Free spins round win is awarded to the player after the round completes.
Free spins round total win in the history contains the whole win of the cycle.
The theoretical RTP of this game when playing in OLYMPUS mode is {0}%
The theoretical RTP of this game when playing in HADES mode is {0}%
The RTP of the game when using "BUY FREE SPINS" in OLYMPUS mode is {0}%
The RTP of the game when using "BUY SUPER FREE SPINS" in OLYMPUS mode is {0}%
The RTP of the game when using "BUY FREE SPINS" in HADES mode is {0}%
The RTP of the game when using "BUY SUPER FREE SPINS" in HADES mode is {0}%

Pokud se bhem kola objev jakkoli symbol WILD, roz se na cel vle a zsk nhodn nsobi se stejnmi monmi hodnotami jako v zkladn he. Tento rozen symbol WILD zstane na obrazovce po celou dobu trvn otoen zdarma.
Hry s vysokou volatilitou vyplc v prmru mn asto, ale zrove pin vy anci doshnout vysokch vher za krtkou dobu.
Toto jsou ROZIUJC SE symboly WILD. Objevujs e na vech vlcch.
Objevuje se na vech vlcch.
MAXIMLN SZKA:
Hr si me vybrat ze dvou hernch profil nazvanch OLYMP a HDES. Vzhled hry se bude mnit podle toho, jak hern profil si vyberete.
V ppad zvady se vechny vplaty a hry ru.
ROZIUJC SE SYMBOLY WILD S NSOBIEM
Teoretick nvratnost tto hry v reimu OLYMP je {0} %.
V reimu OLYMPUS jsou k dispozici nsledujc monosti nkupu:
VOLATILITA
Toto jsou symboly SCATTER. Objevuj se pouze na vlcch 1, 3 a 5 a pouze v zkladn he.

Vechny symboly vyplc na vybranch vhernch linich zleva doprava.
Vhra z otoen zdarma je pitena k vhe z vhern linie.
Vechny vhry se nsob szkou na linii.

Kdykoli se nkter z tchto symbol objev v zkladn he nebo v OTOENCH ZDARMA a rozen by pineslo jakoukoli vhru, symbol WILD zapln cel vlec vertikln a zsk nhodn nsobi. Mon hodnoty nsobie jsou 2x, 3x, 4x, 5x, 6x, 7x, 8x, 9x, 10x, 20x, 25x, 50x a 100x.
Za 300x celkov szky zskte speciln funkci OTOEN ZDARMA, ve kter zaruen padne jeden roziujc se symbol WILD s nhodnm multipliktorem a na nhodn pozici pi prvnm otoen kola zdarma.
MAXIMLN VHRA
V reimu HADES jsou k dispozici nsledujc monosti nkupu:
Pi he v reimu OLYMP bude ance zskat speciln funkci s OTOENMI ZDARMA vy, ale prmrn vhra z kola s OTOENMI ZDARMA bude ni.
RTP hry pi pouit reimu "NAKOUPIT SUPER OTOEN ZDARMA" v reimu HADES je {0} %.
PRAVIDLA HRY
Pokud vyhrajete na nkolika vhernch linich, pitou se do celkov vhry vechny vhry.
RTP hry pi pouit reimu "NAKOUPIT SUPER OTOEN ZDARMA" v reimu OLYMPUS je {0} %.
Vechny symboly vyplc na sousedcch vlcch zleva doprava ponaje vlcem nejvc vlevo.
RTP hry pi pouit reimu "NAKOUPIT OTOEN ZDARMA" v reimu HADES je {0} %.
Za 75x celkov szky zskte standardn funkci OTOEN ZDARMA.
PRAVIDLA HRY
OTOEN ZDARMA
Teoretick nvratnost tto hry v reimu HDES je {0} %.
Vechny hodnoty jsou vyjdeny jako skuten vhry v mincch.
ZAKOUPIT OTOEN ZDARMA

Maximln vhra je v zkladn he i v otoench zdarma omezena na {0}nsobek szky. Pokud celkov vhra v kole s OTOENMI ZDARMA doshne {1}nsobku szky, kolo okamit skon, vyhran stka se pite a vechna zbvajc otoen zdarma propadnou.
Vhra z kola s otoenmi zdarma je hri pipsna po skonen kola.
Kdy zskte 3 symboly SCATTER, spustte tm speciln funkci s OTOENMI ZDARMA a zskte 10 otoen zdarma.
Bhem speciln funkce jsou ve he speciln vlce.
Za 300x celkov szky zskte speciln funkci OTOEN ZDARMA, ve kter zaruen padne jeden roziujc se symbol WILD s nhodnm multipliktorem a na nhodn pozici pi prvnm otoen kola zdarma.
Vhra z kola s otoenmi zdarma je v historii uvedena jako vhra za cel cyklus.
Za 150x celkov szky zskte standardn funkci OTOEN ZDARMA.
Kolo OTOEN ZDARMA me bt okamit sputno ze zkladn hry tm, e je zakoupeno.
Na kad linii je vyplacena pouze nejvy vhra.
RTP hry pi pouit  "NAKOUPIT OTOEN ZDARMA" v reimu OLYMPUS je {0} %.
Speciln funkci nelze spustit znovu.
Nsobi se vztahuje na vechny vhern kombinace, kterch je soust. Pokud bude soust jedn vhern kombinace vce ne jeden symbol WILD, jejich nsobie se setou.
Pi he v reimu HDES bude ance zskat speciln funkci s OTOENMI ZDARMA ni, ale prmrn vhra z kola s OTOENMI ZDARMA bude vy.
MINIMLN SZKA:
